title: added more tests for incoming signals
message: added more tests for incoming signals

title: added support for incoming OSC messages.
message:
added support for incoming OSC messages.

AVAILABLE MESSAGE FORMATS

for Button controller, N = {1..16}
/btnN/msgButtonPressed <args ...>
/btnN/msgButtonReleased <args..>
/btnN/triggerOnButtonReleased <1/0>

for Toggle controllers, N = {1..8}
/togN/msgToggledOn <args >
/togN/msgToggledOff <args>
/togN/value <1/0>

for SeekBar controllers, N = {1..4}
/sbN/range <min> <max>
/sbN/msgValueChanged <args>
/sbN/value <val>

To save OSC settings
/save

also updated to JavaOSC-0.3

title: changed showDialog methods into dialogfragments
message:
changed showDialog methods into dialogfragments

refactored network dialog to a fragment

getting rid of deprecated way of showing dialogs from menu option
selection. changed createNetworkDialog to call the new
NetworkDialogFragment class and handles network settings change on
callback.

refactored about me dialog to a fragment

getting rid of deprecated way of showing dialogs from menu option
selection. changed createAboutDialog to call the new
AboutMeDialogFragment class and handles donate and rate actions on
callback.

refactored wifi settings dialog to a fragment

getting rid of deprecated way of showing dialogs from menu option
selection. changed createWifiAlertDialog to call the new
WifiSettingsDialogFragment class and handles the onWifiSettingsRequested
callback.
